text: Nizhnesaitovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Bakayevsky Selsoviet, Kushnarenkovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 106 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 27 km from Kushnarenkovo, 3 km from Bakayevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kushnarenkovsky District
title: Nizhnesaitovo
